# Sensitive business documents — do NOT push to GitHub
*.pdf
*.pages
*.pptx
*.zip
W9*
*Invoice*
*Contract*
*contract*

# Media assets (large files in project root only)
/*.png
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.avif

# Allow images inside public/ for the website
!public/**/*.jpg
!public/**/*.png
!public/**/*.jpeg
!public/**/*.avif
!public/**/*.webp

# Extracted archives
mahjcard/
# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

